@node "Document_1" "INFO.."
Why another Pack?? Because I wanted it, and since I like Cracktro's I
decided to make CrackPack, A pack containing only Crack-tro's.

If you have some cracktro's lying around, then just send them to the address
given below,and your name will be mentioned in the next pack.(Now, ain't
that something you've always wanted??) But above all, you will get the
latest crackpack before the official release date.

I already have enough Cracktro's to release Issue 2, but I think I'll
release that in a month orso..

                  -==[ Send Cracktro's and stuff to ]==-

                           -=[ oRLINGO/rOYAL ]=-

                               Paul Rietveld
                         Willem Alexanderstraat 6
                            3258 BB  Den Bommel
                              The Netherlands

                     Hip-Hop fans are also welcome...
@endnode

